Interface ISubscriberListener

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICompetitorsListener, IConnectionStatusListener, IControlPassingsListener, IControlPointPositionListener, IControlRouteChangeListener, IControlsListener, IEventMessageListener, IPositionListener, IPositionOffsetListener, IPositionSnappedListener, IRacesListener, IRaceStartStopTimesChangeListener, IRoutesListener, IServerTimeListener, IStartStopTimesChangeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ISubscriberListener

    All the listeners that are used for the consumer application in order to receive events from the server side have to implemented this interface.
